'''菲利普斯埃克塞特学院'''（{{lang-en|Phillips Exeter Academy}}，简称'''PEA'''，又称'''埃克塞特'''），是一所[[私立|私立]][[预科学校|预科学校]]，提供9-12年级及毕业后一年（PG）的教育。学院位于[[美国|美国]][[新罕布什尔州|新罕布什尔州]][[埃克塞特_(新罕布什尔州)|埃克塞特]]镇，是[[十校联盟|十校联盟]]成员之一。学院建校久远，因其历史、影响力、财富和学术声誉，被诸多媒体称为美国的精英学校之一。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.businessinsider.com/most-elite-boarding-schools-in-america-2016-2|title=The 50 most elite boarding schools in America|last=Loudenback|first=Emmie Martin, Tanza|website=Business Insider|access-date=2020-03-24}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.niche.com/k12/search/best-boarding-high-schools/|title=2020 Best Boarding High Schools in America|website=Niche|language=en|access-date=2020-03-24}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.npr.org/sections/ed/2017/05/03/526769862/elite-prep-schools-experiment-with-all-gender-dorms|title=Elite Prep Schools Experiment With 'All-Gender' Dorms|website=NPR.org|language=en|access-date=2020-03-24}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|date=1996|title=The Status of African Americans at the Nation's Most Prestigious Boarding Schools|journal=The Journal of Blacks in Higher Education|issue=14|pages=26–28|doi=10.2307/2962808|jstor=2962808|issn=1077-3711}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.businessinsider.in/mark-zuckerberg-attended-the-most-elite-boarding-school-in-america/articleshow/51082462.cms|title=Mark Zuckerberg attended the most elite boarding school in America|website=Business Insider|access-date=2020-03-24}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|last=Fabrikant|first=Geraldine|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2008/01/26/business/26prep.html|title=At Elite Prep Schools, College-Size Endowments|date=2008-01-26|work=The New York Times|access-date=2020-03-24|language=en-US|issn=0362-4331}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.thetelegraph.com/technology/businessinsider/article/Booths-Full-Of-Booze-Electric-Mermaids-And-6006613.php|title=What it's like to attend Phillips Exeter Academy, one of the most elite boarding schools in America|last=Robinson|first=Melia|last2=By|first2=Provided|date=2019-